---
title: Crumbed Katsu Chicken Sando with Fries & Creamy Slaw
description: Do you know what we really love and can’t wait to get our hands on, a good sando. Whip up your favourite version with crumbed
chicken strips drizzled in a rich katsu sauce and slaw. Add a side of fries to complete the classic sandwich shop feel.
